snippet.title: DragonBox Algebra - Official Trailer (2014)
snippet.description:
Find out how you can learn algebra by playing a video game. DragonBox Algebra teaches players as young as five how to solve equations without prerequisites.

Read more: http://wewanttoknow.com/algebra/
